    old "{#ch4_main_7f03563e}"
    new "It's already Sunday."

    old "{#ch4_main_e8881ae0}"
    new "I've been getting increasingly anxious about Natsuki's upcoming visit."

    old "{#ch4_main_1e3fd2be}"
    new "I keep telling myself there's no reason to be nervous, but it doesn't help much."

    old "{#ch4_main_d63e1a44}"
    new "I wonder if she'll act any different when it's just the two of us?"

    old "{#ch4_main_c1d95768}"
    new "Meanwhile, she's been texting me a lot."

    old "{#ch4_main_a36be6d2}"
    new "We sent each other one after exchanging numbers to double-check, but it turned into conversation."

    old "{#ch4_main_4ac86efe}"
    new "She's almost a different personality on the phone, using tons of emoji and cute language."

    old "{#ch4_main_51122e85}"
    new "She also really likes complaining about things, but I kind of saw that one coming."

    old "{#ch4_main_54fc51cb}"
    new "But putting Natsuki aside..."

    old "{#ch4_main_533ca6d9}"
    new "I've been getting increasingly anxious about Yuri's upcoming visit."

    old "{#ch4_main_1e3fd2be_1}"
    new "I keep telling myself there's no reason to be nervous, but it doesn't help much."

    old "{#ch4_main_6a261072}"
    new "Yuri is clearly an introvert and also an intimate person in general."

    old "{#ch4_main_172e5fe9}"
    new "There's no doubt that she'll open up a little bit when it's just the two of us."

    old "{#ch4_main_dcb4a9fe}"
    new "Meanwhile, we've even been texting occasionally."

    old "{#ch4_main_c1a6e593}"
    new "She was extremely apprehensive at first, but it wasn't long before I was already learning more about her."

    old "{#ch4_main_3adbf0d5}"
    new "But putting Yuri aside..."

    old "{#ch4_main_e9699a3e}"
    new "I haven't heard a thing from Sayori since she left club early the other day."

    old "{#ch4_main_25706431}"
    new "It's not like we text each other all the time or anything..."

    old "{#ch4_main_8e3af5cc}"
    new "But I've been worried about her in the back of my mind."

    old "{#ch4_main_77697156}"
    new "Between what Sayori said, and what Monika said..."

    old "{#ch4_main_be038b9e}"
    new "Is it really okay for me to put Sayori's feelings aside when she might need me?"

    old "{#ch4_main_29ce83ba}"
    new "I decide to visit Sayori before [ch4_name] comes over."

    old "{#ch4_main_f5e89c18}"
    new "Rather than asking, I simply tell her \"I'm coming over\", much like we've done in the past."

    old "{#ch4_main_b6b01504}"
    new "Once I reach Sayori's house, I knock on the door before entering it myself."

    old "{#ch4_main_f3cf9c85}"
    new "Again, we used to play so often that we've made it a habit of simply entering each other's houses like we were family."

    old "{#ch4_main_d02cb356}"
    new "The house is quiet."

    old "{#ch4_main_ba76d2b3}"
    new "Sayori isn't anywhere on the first floor, so I assume she's up in her room."

    old "{#ch4_main_122612c2}"
    new "It's already strange of her not to run down and greet me."

    old "{#ch4_main_cfd27d7b}"
    new "I head up to her bedroom, where I finally find her."

    old "{#ch4_main_e766b9e2}"
    new "\"Sayori?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_168027c8}"
    new "\"Hi [player]~\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d5c40262}"
    new "I sit down in her room."

    old "{#ch4_main_cde4b14b}"
    new "Sayori forces a smile, but it's easy to tell that she's different."

    old "{#ch4_main_60097b82}"
    new "There's a minute of silence between us."

    old "{#ch4_main_91dd180c}"
    new "\"You haven't come over like this in a long time, have you?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_39957f69}"
    new "\"Ah... I guess you're right.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_bbd67548}"
    new "\"It has been a long time.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_9f9c925d}"
    new "\"Not much has really changed, has it?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_3e8f239e}"
    new "Sayori's room is as messy as it's always been."

    old "{#ch4_main_aebaa3fb}"
    new "I also recognize the same stuffed animals and wall decorations that she's had for years now."

    old "{#ch4_main_506cc7c0}"
    new "\"Ehehe~\""

    old "{#ch4_main_a8c5f7d4}"
    new "\"If you came over more often, it wouldn't be such a mess.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_7d0484ac}"
    new "\"That's because I end up cleaning it for you...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c067efa9}"
    new "\"How come you suddenly wanted to come over today?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_9e1f01a3}"
    new "\"Aren't you supposed to see [ch4_name] today?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_3f1ca1d2}"
    new "\"Yeah, but...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_5f378027}"
    new "\"...Wait, how did you know that?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_be7d338c}"
    new "Sayori had already left by the time we decided that last meeting."

    old "{#ch4_main_aad7ca62}"
    new "\"Monika told me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c3ad1529}"
    new "\"It's only natural for her to keep me informed about the festival preparations, right?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_29886549}"
    new "\"Ah, that's true...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_0e65e446}"
    new "\"But what about you?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_230aada7}"
    new "\"Aren't you going to be helping Monika today?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_8bbf088c}"
    new "\"Of course!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ce469512}"
    new "\"But I'm just helping her online.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_755e2699}"
    new "\"We didn't plan to meet up or anything.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_95fc3bb8}"
    new "\"Ah, so it's just me and [ch4_name], then...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_df50d1be}"
    new "\"Yep~\""

    old "{#ch4_main_fab2261a}"
    new "There's more silence between us."

    old "{#ch4_main_afd64660}"
    new "Sayori stares in a random direction."

    old "{#ch4_main_ee146ae9}"
    new "Everything about her behavior is really uncharacteristic."

    old "{#ch4_main_ddfa6b61}"
    new "I finally get to the point."

    old "{#ch4_main_34fdc6c8}"
    new "\"I just...wanted to see how you were doing.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_a133cd63}"
    new "\"After you left on Friday.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_75a9201e}"
    new "\"When something's wrong, you can't hide it from me!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c9b70b7c}"
    new "\"I know you too well.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_cb70afb1}"
    new "\"So...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6a9ba0ff}"
    new "Sayori smiles, shaking her head."

    old "{#ch4_main_55b00119}"
    new "\"That's no good, [player].\""

    old "{#ch4_main_fb2e5377}"
    new "\"Eh?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e30500ac}"
    new "\"Why can't it just be like it's always been?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_628ab9fa}"
    new "\"This is all my fault.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_1e5e72c5}"
    new "\"If I didn't get so weak and accidentally express my feelings...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_f419234b}"
    new "\"If I didn't make that stupid mistake...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d9944342}"
    new "\"Then you wouldn't have been worried about me at all.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c2ee41ba}"
    new "\"You wouldn't have come here.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_64624b6c}"
    new "\"You wouldn't have even been thinking about me right now.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_05305f6c}"
    new "\"But this...is just my punishment, isn't it?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_35b0930c}"
    new "\"I'm getting punished for being so selfish.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_34af1de7}"
    new "\"I think that's why the world decided to have you come over today.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_7db33577}"
    new "\"It just wants to torture me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_51280e41}"
    new "\"Ehehe~\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ce62c226}"
    new "\"Sayori!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_b91a73e8}"
    new "I grab Sayori by the shoulders."

    old "{#ch4_main_20fe6359}"
    new "\"What on Earth are you saying?!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_cbefa080}"
    new "\"Are you listening to yourself right now?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_8246ee4c}"
    new "\"I know something happened to you.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_5e1b9bed}"
    new "\"There's no other explanation for you to be like this.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d778b065}"
    new "\"So tell me, already...!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_5efb74b0}"
    new "\"Until I know, I won't be able to stop thinking about it!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_08a841a6}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_81d59952}"
    new "\"Ahaha...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6dbc946c}"
    new "Sayori gives me an empty smile."

    old "{#ch4_main_95b305ce}"
    new "\"You really put me in a trap, [player].\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c9170687}"
    new "\"But...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_05d3b914}"
    new "\"You're wrong.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_984fcfac}"
    new "\"Nothing happened to me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_3eab9950}"
    new "\"I've always been like this.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_07fedd4b}"
    new "\"You're just seeing it for the first time.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d540c013}"
    new "\"Seeing what?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_5ae14a76}"
    new "\"What are you talking about, Sayori?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_67281b29}"
    new "\"Ehehe~\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c05b8cdb}"
    new "\"You're really just going to make me say it, aren't you, [player]?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_58e8d872}"
    new "\"I guess I have no choice this time.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_068d9aad}"
    new "\"The thing is...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_b9a43929}"
    new "\"I've had really bad depression my whole life.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_54937bac}"
    new "\"Did you know that?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_bc5feba5}"
    new "\"Why do you think I'm late to school every day?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_968d7c40}"
    new "\"Because most days, I can't even find a reason to get out of bed.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_fd1c4b3e}"
    new "\"What reason is there to do anything when I fully know how worthless I am?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_86925814}"
    new "\"Why go to school?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_3120cbcb}"
    new "\"Why eat?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ce05cc1f}"
    new "\"Why make friends?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_b8110758}"
    new "\"Why make other people put their energy and caring to waste by having them spend it on me?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_49b2decf}"
    new "\"That's what it feels like.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_b903ffad}"
    new "\"And that's why I just want to make everyone happy...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d624f808}"
    new "\"Without anyone worrying about me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_2b35b6fe}"
    new "\"...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_42dbe169}"
    new "I'm in shock."

    old "{#ch4_main_f9ec361d}"
    new "I can't even figure out how to respond."

    old "{#ch4_main_cdec7507}"
    new "How is it possible that Sayori kept this from me the entire time that I've known her?"

    old "{#ch4_main_aa509b9c}"
    new "Did she really want so badly for me to just not think about her?"

    old "{#ch4_main_8af8b405}"
    new "\"...Why, Sayori?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_82fc61d6}"
    new "\"Eh...?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_51dbc2b3}"
    new "\"Why is it that you've never told me about this?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_8d0ee999}"
    new "\"It almost feels like I've been betrayed as your close friend.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_31f6649c}"
    new "\"Because if I knew, I would have done everything I could to support you!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_687c50fd}"
    new "\"Even if there's only so much that I could do...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ae3d12f1}"
    new "\"I would have tried a little bit harder to make every day a little better for you.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_5d52395f}"
    new "\"That's why I'm your friend!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6adfa620}"
    new "\"All you had to do was tell me!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_4c272a4c}"
    new "\"You don't understand at all, [player].\""

    old "{#ch4_main_eb166bd5}"
    new "\"Why do you think I didn't tell you?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e2f0904b}"
    new "\"Because if I told you, then you would have to waste effort caring about me instead of doing important things.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ecd4d1f8}"
    new "\"I don't want to be cared about.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ae9dc47d}"
    new "\"It's bittersweet, when people try to care about me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e40d4b16}"
    new "\"It feels nice sometimes.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ad157485}"
    new "\"But it also feels like a bat being swung against my head.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_01289f61}"
    new "\"Ahaha~\""

    old "{#ch4_main_9911b1e5}"
    new "\"That's why I wanted so badly for you to make friends with everyone else...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_1981af56}"
    new "\"Helping everyone be happy together is the best thing for me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_7b6aa8b2}"
    new "\"But then, I discovered something else, too.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_9374b73b}"
    new "\"Seeing you make friends and get closer with everyone in the club...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_77d5d91b}"
    new "\"It feels like a spear going through my heart.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_dba77a8d}"
    new "\"So, that's why.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6dbfc55a}"
    new "\"That's why I decided the world just wants to torture me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_5f8787ec}"
    new "\"Every path leads to nothing but hurt.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_1f3198b0}"
    new "\"Ahaha~\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d753d516}"
    new "\"You're right that I don't understand...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_2def5ee1}"
    new "\"I don't understand your feelings at all, Sayori.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ad069b67}"
    new "\"But I don't need to understand.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_dce0f10f}"
    new "\"Whatever it takes for me to help you stop hurting...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_dbb6df0a}"
    new "\"That's what I'll do.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_4d3f0c17}"
    new "\"No, [player].\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6918a69b}"
    new "\"There's nothing.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_358610db}"
    new "\"Nothing at all.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e65deda1}"
    new "\"The only thing that could have helped is if everything could be like it always was.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_45fcd8d1}"
    new "\"But I was selfish.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6dfe5599}"
    new "\"I finally showed you what a horrible person I am.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_a1d72cb2}"
    new "Tears streak down Sayori's face."

    old "{#ch4_main_6941b385}"
    new "\"I made you join the literature club because I was selfish.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_51691290}"
    new "\"And I was punished by my heart hurting in a way that I couldn't understand.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_3874471a}"
    new "\"And now you came here and I made you hurt, too.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_7eb1ddf6}"
    new "\"I'm just weak and selfish.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_3d05c6aa}"
    new "\"That's all I am.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e8a03dc8}"
    new "\"And that's why I'm going to accept these punishments.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_a8841dc8}"
    new "\"Because I deserve every last one...!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_78e5f68c}"
    new "Without thinking, I once again grab Sayori's shoulders."

    old "{#ch4_main_af8cb833}"
    new "This time, I pull her into a tight embrace."

    old "{#ch4_main_23743af4}"
    new "\"A-Ah--\""

    old "{#ch4_main_23d81314}"
    new "\"[player]...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_bf3e34d4}"
    new "\"Sayori.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6c10d11d}"
    new "\"I don't care if you feel selfish.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d279c67d}"
    new "\"I'm really happy that you convinced me to join the club.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_7dffacc8}"
    new "\"Seeing you every day makes it worthwhile enough.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_4fd890e4}"
    new "\"If I make friends with everyone else, then that's just a bonus.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_606cd387}"
    new "\"But please never underestimate how much I care about you.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_834094f7}"
    new "\"I wouldn't have it any other way.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_23d81314_1}"
    new "\"[player]...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_97239717}"
    new "Sayori isn't hugging me back."

    old "{#ch4_main_0d7e9765}"
    new "Despite my arms being wrapped around her, Sayori's arms remain at her sides."

    old "{#ch4_main_75921590}"
    new "She starts sobbing next to my ear."

    old "{#ch4_main_fd408bf7}"
    new "\"No...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_12f97b41}"
    new "\"Don't do this...to me...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_93c5b869}"
    new "\"Please don't do this...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_23d81314_2}"
    new "\"[player]...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e8a331c8}"
    new "\"I...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_dcc226a3}"
    new "Sayori barely manages to speak between her sobs."

    old "{#ch4_main_451f1671}"
    new "I don't know if I'm doing the right thing."

    old "{#ch4_main_8709e79b}"
    new "But all I want is for her to know that I care."

    old "{#ch4_main_9e467023}"
    new "\"If you have it in you to call yourself selfish, then you have to let me be selfish too.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_211c4d9a}"
    new "\"No matter what it takes, I'll figure out what needs to change.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e00b981c}"
    new "\"I'll make these feelings go away.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_4e1a31b1}"
    new "\"And if there's anything that you need me to do...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e46ea2e5}"
    new "\"Then you'd better tell me.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_62646328}"
    new "\"I'll get mad if you don't.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e1554201}"
    new "\"...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e12a63c3}"
    new "\"I...don't know...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d9c81ff9}"
    new "\"I don't know...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_61ecc309}"
    new "\"I don't know.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6f0a7265}"
    new "Gently, Sayori finally puts her arms around me in return."

    old "{#ch4_main_d37409b2}"
    new "\"I don't know anything.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ceb757fb}"
    new "\"It's all really scary...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_b17fbfd7}"
    new "\"I don't understand any of my feelings, [player]...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c6417526}"
    new "\"The only time I'm not feeling nothing is when I'm feeling pain.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c9170687_1}"
    new "\"But...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_16e388fe}"
    new "\"Your hugs are so warm...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_9b224a34}"
    new "\"...And that's really scary, too.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_6e1bca9b}"
    new "Sayori lets me go."

    old "{#ch4_main_43a2a362}"
    new "As she does so, I let her go as well."

    old "{#ch4_main_dd6142ec}"
    new "\"The festival is tomorrow.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d06a9bfe}"
    new "\"Yeah...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_de06eb82}"
    new "\"It's going to be fun, right?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_036bd57a}"
    new "\"Yeah.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_684b10e4}"
    new "\"How would you like for me to spend it all with you?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_c17de943}"
    new "\"U-Um...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_57cb4d56}"
    new "\"Ah--\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ceb1f637}"
    new "\"It's what I want.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_0a4dbc8d}"
    new "\"I promise.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_23615804}"
    new "\"I...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_f334bfcb}"
    new "\"I think that would be nice, then...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_cf1adef2}"
    new "\"Yeah.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_ad6d9b2c}"
    new "Sayori wipes her eyes."

    old "{#ch4_main_2efa6d9b}"
    new "If I could spend the whole day here, I would."

    old "{#ch4_main_0d36eb63}"
    new "\"Of all days, this has to be the one where I have other plans...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_e068d329}"
    new "\"Maybe I should cancel--\""

    old "{#ch4_main_8a85c027}"
    new "\"No, don't--!\""

    old "{#ch4_main_7e7ed6dc}"
    new "\"Please don't...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_fcaef8fa}"
    new "\"If you did that...then I really wouldn't forgive you.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_fc896afd}"
    new "\"But...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_0756728a}"
    new "\"It's almost time for [ch4_name] to meet me at my house...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_95533e69}"
    new "\"At the very least, do you want to come along and help out?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_4d4bb695}"
    new "\"It would be fun.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_57d1a9b9}"
    new "To my surprise, Sayori shakes her head."

    old "{#ch4_main_3bf26e9f}"
    new "\"I'm sorry.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_771c1295}"
    new "\"I don't know if that would be very good for me today.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_75d2f9e7}"
    new "\"You understand, right?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_93deaf69}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_main_d8b1d200}"
    new "\"It's...kind of hard for me to fully understand.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_81f13121}"
    new "\"But I'm trying my hardest.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_61c2e6b9}"
    new "\"It's okay.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_b3911918}"
    new "\"Don't worry too much about it.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_394a0e83}"
    new "\"I'll see you tomorrow, okay?\""

    old "{#ch4_main_44977a95}"
    new "\"...Alright.\""

    old "{#ch4_main_9c940590}"
    new "\"I look forward to it.\""

