    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b2f21f7b}"
    new "\"Intense...?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cbaeb1a4}"
    new "\"I guess that's the best way to put it.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_49d2b152}"
    new "\"Is that...a bad thing?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4f671c67}"
    new "\"No, not at all.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_0137eca8}"
    new "\"It's something that I like about you, actually.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f6874ccc}"
    new "\"I-Is that so...?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_af3e9355}"
    new "\"That makes me feel relieved...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9854966a}"
    new "\"And kind of happy...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_94800631}"
    new "\"Yeah, no need to be so anxious.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b7d344a1}"
    new "\"You can relax a little.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_bf43dc27}"
    new "\"Relax...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d1d227e2}"
    new "\"I brought some things for relaxation.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6d7bbfcd}"
    new "\"I was going to use them during the poetry event...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_66eaf3e1}"
    new "\"Oh yeah? Like what?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4d80474c}"
    new "\"Let's see...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ccdd61a2}"
    new "Yuri rummages through her bag."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_e00058c5}"
    new "She pulls out a few candles and a wooden cylinder-shaped object."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f5ca2c9a}"
    new "\"I did some shopping on the way here, so I happen to have these in my bag.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_765dad15}"
    new "\"I planned to cover the windows in black paper and use the candles to light the room.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f943cc13}"
    new "\"I think that would be amazing, don't you?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_fbd5c4bc}"
    new "\"Yeah, that would be really neat.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_773a7b7c}"
    new "\"What's that wooden thing, though?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_84103177}"
    new "\"Oh, this?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_46615e83}"
    new "\"It's a diffuser for essential oils.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c46fb0b4}"
    new "\"How familiar are you with aromatherapy?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c4714615}"
    new "\"Not familiar at all...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_0ac10b23}"
    new "\"Ah, is that so?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_160fc237}"
    new "\"It's one of my favorite contributors to a positive atmosphere.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7e0d9b6c}"
    new "\"Depending on the oils or herbs you choose, you can change the mood of the air itself.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_68bd94eb}"
    new "\"You can even feel it permeate through your body.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7a8bf27b}"
    new "\"Relaxation, positive energy, romance, reflection...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_63fcc9ac}"
    new "\"It's almost like magic.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_fb4f44e1}"
    new "Yuri takes the cylinder and pushes a switch on the bottom."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7107b767}"
    new "In just a moment, a thin ray of vapor begins to spout through a small hole on the top."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_390de38c}"
    new "\"Wow, that smells wonderful.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4b18a6dc}"
    new "\"What kind of mood is that one for?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_34d80b06}"
    new "\"This is a Jasmine essential oil.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_24a8c22a}"
    new "\"It smells a little sweet and flowery, right?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b87d6070}"
    new "\"Yeah, that's a good way to describe it.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d48abd3c}"
    new "\"I chose Jasmine for the event because it provides more than relaxation.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_885223a6}"
    new "\"Jasmine enhances your emotions and helps you feel them flow through your body.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_edccefe6}"
    new "\"You feel warmer, and your heart pounds more heavily.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_68c0a0ec}"
    new "\"Don't you think that will be perfect for sharing our poems?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_dab38280}"
    new "\"It does sound suitable...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_8aa7202d}"
    new "\"But you seem to know a lot about this, so I'll trust your opinion with anything.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_93d659fb}"
    new "Yuri smiles gently, clearly enjoying herself."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_50fae775}"
    new "She again reaches into her bag and pulls out several spools of thin ribbon."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b62d580c}"
    new "\"What are those for?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cc60637c}"
    new "\"Well...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_e9e9de52}"
    new "\"Did you purchase the origami paper I asked you to get?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ffcd40a2}"
    new "\"Yeah, I have it over here...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_47353469}"
    new "\"We won't be using the paper for folding origami.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_22eae3a4}"
    new "\"What I'd like to do is write a different word on each paper.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_22ab5158}"
    new "\"We'll need about a hundred of them.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4f43e9fe}"
    new "\"Oh yeah?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2de638ab}"
    new "\"What will those be used for?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_43945948}"
    new "\"Well, I'm going to cut pieces of ribbon to hang from the doorway of the classroom.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c3c62ae5}"
    new "\"Then, we can fasten the paper onto the ribbons to create a doorway curtain.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_91b54924}"
    new "\"Wouldn't that be beautiful?\""

