    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ce018b3a}"
    new "\"That's really creative!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d51182dd}"
    new "\"I had no idea you'd be so good at this, Yuri.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a9eb75bc}"
    new "\"Is...that so?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_53203fa3}"
    new "\"Well, I suppose I do get a little intense...as you'd put it.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_e43fd5a9}"
    new "\"Uhuhu.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cdc817ae}"
    new "Yuri giggles with red cheeks."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_19e0a918}"
    new "Is it just me, or is she more relaxed when it's just the two of us?"

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6ad7399d}"
    new "Or maybe it's the excitement she feels from sharing something that she enjoys."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ca3f9b5a}"
    new "\"Here's a marker, [player].\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3b16a249}"
    new "\"You can write any characters you want.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_58cb4240}"
    new "\"I'll help you once I finish cutting the ribbons.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_eeadee1b}"
    new "\"Ah, alright.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3a9138bb}"
    new "Sitting on the floor together, the two of us get to work."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_52e58580}"
    new "I carefully draw a different character on each paper, doing my best to manage my bad handwriting."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_dd943745}"
    new "Yuri unravels a long strand of red ribbon to her desired length."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1cc8a003}"
    new "Then, she reaches into her bag once more and pulls out a pocket knife."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_bbe4458e}"
    new "\"Eh...?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9588fb2b}"
    new "The knife is strangely beautiful."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_42062e86}"
    new "The silver handle has an intricate pattern of waves etched into it."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_dfd6bcd4}"
    new "The blade itself is gently tinted blue."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_78f3868f}"
    new "\"That's no ordinary pocket knife...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_93a46c5e}"
    new "\"It looks really fancy.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9b47ae2d}"
    new "\"A-Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ae7f22e8}"
    new "\"Well...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_be7d4ca7}"
    new "Embarrassed, Yuri looks away."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_def0ad19}"
    new "\"What is it?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cbdd802c}"
    new "\"You're going to think it's weird...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_34c5d38d}"
    new "\"Yuri, whatever it is, I have no reason to judge.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5e0b9d41}"
    new "\"To each their own, you know?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6901b8aa}"
    new "\"If you promise you won't be weirded out...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5f1cf882}"
    new "\"Yeah, I promise.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a8fab8b1}"
    new "\"Alright...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4791d5bf}"
    new "\"The thing is, I'm kind of into knives...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4959c25f}"
    new "\"They're just...so pretty...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ea47e2ed}"
    new "\"I-I can't help it!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ea5c6bb2}"
    new "\"I don't know what it is...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_585a09bb}"
    new "\"The combination of craftsmanship and feeling of danger, maybe...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1035f297}"
    new "\"Uu, what am I saying...?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5053aa7a}"
    new "\"Please don't think I'm weird for this...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ee7d9dbd}"
    new "\"Ahaha.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4a73dfe6}"
    new "\"You're laughing at me...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ebf61b90}"
    new "\"No, I'm not laughing at you.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_8436c3fc}"
    new "\"It's just funny how nervous you got about sharing.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_98e5019e}"
    new "\"It's...well, it's an interesting thing to be into, I guess.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2bdc4458}"
    new "\"But I think it kind of suits you.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_13cf2b15}"
    new "\"Suits me...?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_515d3ad5}"
    new "\"Yeah... It's kind of intense. Ahaha.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d53d688b}"
    new "\"Besides, it's a really cool-looking knife, I can't deny that.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_26589eeb}"
    new "\"It is, isn't it...?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9ec1744f}"
    new "Yuri relaxes her expression once again."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_536b8e3f}"
    new "\"Would you like to hold it?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2a490275}"
    new "\"Sure, I'll check it out.\""

