    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a5b6534a}"
    new "I take it and turn it around in my hands."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b73b12fb}"
    new "It feels heavy, and extremely solid."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5e2013d8}"
    new "Where do you even get a knife like this...?"

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b6c65002}"
