    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_684804a5}"
    new "\"I'm sorry, I'm sorry...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_93deaf69}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5545b90b}"
    new "Sure, it was a little weird, and it took me by surprise..."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c4cc71cf}"
    new "But I guess she was just trying to help, right...?"

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_0b0e5f5b}"
    new "\"Yuri, I think you're overreacting a little...\""

