    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f65e23a4}"
    new "It looks better than I expected and will be very effective as a door curtain."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_135a7724}"
    new "\"It looks great.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6fd41911}"
    new "\"Good thinking coming up with this, Yuri.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_672fb4b2}"
    new "\"Ah, thanks...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_586312e0}"
    new "\"It's just something I saw online, really.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cebe4068}"
    new "\"Are you ready to move onto the next task?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_39ef9b02}"
    new "\"Yeah, let's do it.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_068582fd}"
    new "\"What do you have in mind?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6fb26d3d}"
    new "\"I'd like to create a banner.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_dfef5d98}"
    new "\"That's why I asked you to buy the paint tablets.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_96a57d25}"
    new "\"Ah, that's right.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4d3528f0}"
    new "One of the items Yuri had asked me to buy was a kit of watercolor paint tablets."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_623899fe}"
    new "\"We'll need about six cups of water to put each of the tablets in.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_823c4f64}"
    new "\"Do you mind fetching those for us?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c2eb53da}"
