    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_50bc645c}"
    new "\"If you fill the cups too much, it will be too diluted.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b093d7f5}"
    new "Taking Yuri's advice, I decide to use small plastic bathroom cups rather than full-sized glasses."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b961b16f}"
    new "I put them on a plate to catch any paint that drips, then bring it back into my room."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a09b77d5}"
    new "\"Yuri?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b83ad773}"
    new "\"Yes?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_efc7b6df}"
    new "I come in to see Yuri quickly unrolling her sleeve, pulling it back over her arm."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ef5f85f4}"
    new "\"Ah, nothing...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9fa41e43}"
    new "\"Your face is a little red.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_675d7d5c}"
    new "\"Is it too hot in here, or anything?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2d1d7d7e}"
    new "\"Ah--\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7a464969}"
    new "\"No, not at all!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a16ccc28}"
    new "\"There's nothing wrong, so...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_db4340a5}"
    new "\"Let's mix the paint.\""

