    new "Yuri hurriedly dismisses me and takes it upon herself to unwrap the tablets, dropping them into the cups."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3e4bce89}"
    new "\"So...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b644a548}"
    new "\"I thought we would do something simple that would look very nice.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6b6d95e8}"
    new "\"I'd like to paint a gradient across the banner...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3f3a93a3}"
    new "\"Starting with the colors for a sunrise, then daytime, then sunset and nighttime.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7b6ef5bc}"
    new "\"Once it dries, I'll write an inspirational quote across the banner.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c969de9e}"
    new "\"We can hang it on the wall behind the podium at the front of the classroom.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_0e82c4ee}"
    new "\"Ah, neat.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_e7727079}"
    new "\"What are you going to write?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_052e996f}"
    new "\"Well...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d95e4e0a}"
    new "\"...It will be more fun to surprise you.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_35fbb699}"
    new "Yuri smiles at me."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_0f240219}"
    new "\"If you say so...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_197498ac}"
    new "After rolling out the banner, Yuri and I kneel on opposite sides so we don't get in the way of each other."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_bd5f479c}"
    new "Yuri uses a brush and adds a few dots of different colors across the banner to serve as a color guide when we paint."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_16905ab4}"
    new "\"This kind of reminds me of elementary school...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_43b22982}"
    new "Painting on a banner with watercolors feels a lot like the art class projects we had back then."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a8b0e464}"
    new "It's relaxing."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_728dcbc5_1}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_56217eb5}"
    new "\"I'm sorry if this feels too childish...!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_be62e824}"
    new "\"No, I didn't mean that at all.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_636d9380}"
    new "\"It's kind of fun, you know?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_e9a8b6f3}"
    new "\"...Yeah.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a022de23}"
    new "\"It is fun.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1dd76b95}"
    new "\"I'm glad you feel that way, too.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d4ca8264}"
    new "Yuri stops painting for a moment, thinking to herself."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c2c620fb}"
    new "\"For me...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_76d4ffa1}"
    new "\"I don't need to go out and do crazy things to have fun.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_33388526}"
    new "\"In fact, I usually don't even want to.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_128efca8}"
    new "\"I just like when I can spend time with one other person...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_005b197c}"
    new "\"Even if it's something simple, like reading - it doesn't even matter if we don't talk much.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4ed83b82}"
    new "\"Just having a friend next to me makes things feel a little bit nicer.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c3bb862b}"
    new "\"I think that's all it takes for me to be happy.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_85d4ab1c}"
    new "\"Is that so...?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b2a4a3d5}"
    new "Even if Yuri and I are quite different, I can understand where she's coming from."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_750d2661}"
    new "I feel that way about things like anime and games, where simply sharing the experience with someone can make me happy."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d0c830b0}"
    new "\"I think I feel the same way.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f1c99cd9}"
    new "Yuri smiles gently."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7bceb5ec}"
    new "\"I knew you'd understand...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_af179c74}"
    new "Yuri leans over the banner to grab an unused paintbrush."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4a901502}"
    new "But I move at the same time, causing my head to bump into hers."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_742c38fe}"
    new "\"Kya--!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c817a551}"
    new "\"S-Sorry!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b5ff971c}"
    new "Yuri reels back, and I quickly lift my hands in surprise."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a80d2f8a}"
    new "\"Are you hurt?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_fb0e853e}"
    new "\"N-No, I'm not hurt.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5aa191a8}"
    new "\"It just startled me...that's all.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cb3ad9b3}"
    new "\"Sorry, I should have asked you to get it for me...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f2a32672}"
    new "\"It's not your fault.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_25d60f82}"
    new "\"Ah, your face...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7127d05f}"
    new "There are droplets of paint on Yuri's face and neck."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7f5dd1f8}"
    new "\"Is there something on my face?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3f00caef}"
    new "\"Yeah, I accidentally got paint on you...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_83e1a6f7}"
    new "\"Sorry, it's totally my fault!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cc6a4c18}"
    new "\"I'll get a towel right away.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_25041c7e}"
    new "I rush out and fetch a small towel, then I dampen it with hot water."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_e1d00546}"
    new "I return to my room and kneel back down in front of her."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c2b67b46}"
    new "\"Here...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ee083efd}"
    new "I pat down Yuri's face and neck with the towel."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_29a199f7}"
    new "\"Ah--\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_34cec937}"
    new "\"Is something wrong?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1a60c448}"
    new "\"It's hot...I just didn't expect it.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4bbe5891}"
    new "\"Sorry...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_251373d4}"
    new "\"I didn't want to use cold water.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_433edcd4}"
    new "Having finished, I start to retract my hand."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_aacf7734}"
    new "But Yuri suddenly holds my wrist."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1899caaf}"
    new "\"Wait--\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_fb2e5377}"
    new "\"Eh?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_15e02934}"
    new "\"Just...for a little longer.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f820c100}"
    new "\"It feels really nice...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_93deaf69_2}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_54dc1c00}"
    new "I keep my hand still against Yuri's neck."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a618dd3d}"
    new "She looks into my eyes."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_52e2ef25}"
    new "It's an intense expression that I recognize from when she reads her books..."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ae3cc4b3}"
    new "Almost as if she's lost in a daze, enveloped by her own thoughts."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6deb9809}"
    new "She breathes gently, half through slightly-parted lips."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2d899e99}"
    new "What is happening...?"

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_45949426}"
    new "Is it the aroma of the Jasmine oil giving me this dizzy feeling?"

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3b6aae32}"
    new "Yuri's gentle fingers, wrapped around my wrist, send a tingling sensation through my arm."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5d16edad}"
    new "And suddenly, her face seems to be much closer to mine than it was just a moment ago..."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_728dcbc5_2}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cda22c45}"
    new "Yuri slowly pulls away."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_485fb852}"
    new "\"Sorry...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_02e9911c}"
    new "\"I've been feeling a little light-headed today.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_696c1815}"
    new "\"I didn't mean to space out...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f7b2a944}"
    new "\"I-It's fine...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a7cbdc20}"
    new "The moment is over as soon as it began."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_959427da}"
    new "Yuri picks up her brush again."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7b6e91a0}"
    new "But her movements seem clumsier, like she's unable to focus."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f6454750}"
    new "I remain silent, forced to ignore the event that just transpired."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_69cc8240}"
    new "I hesitantly retrieve my own brush and continue following Yuri's example."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_583843dd}"
    new "\"That should do it...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3e5faaa7}"
    new "I finish filling the night sky with white dots that look like stars."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_590b6e62}"
    new "Looking at the banner as a whole, it's very pretty and natural-looking."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cef5aee6}"
    new "\"I think it came out better than I expected.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d47ed027}"
    new "\"I'm really happy with the results.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b805585e}"
    new "\"Yeah, me too.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d10cb133}"
    new "\"Are you going to add the lettering now?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_616184f4}"
    new "\"Ah, not yet...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c9640c73}"
    new "\"It needs to dry first.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_af837fea}"
    new "\"That's true, but won't that take a while?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_be96fb6c}"
    new "\"Well...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_58c476fe}"
    new "\"Perhaps it would be best to leave it here, then have you bring it in the morning.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7dcd70d3}"
    new "\"I can do the lettering in the classroom before our event starts.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4f2df90f}"
    new "\"Is that okay?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_bb362cac}"
    new "\"That's totally fine.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_75243184}"
    new "\"Wonderful.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2f957b61}"
    new "\"In that case...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_755f06ea}"
    new "\"I don't think there's anything more for us to do here.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_0c054906}"
    new "\"Phew.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_665032ee}"
    new "\"Ahaha.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_59a18e38}"
    new "\"You say that like you're glad it's over.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a02df21f}"
    new "\"Was I wrong to assume that you were at least enjoying yourself a little bit?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ecfaa6be}"
    new "\"Ah, no, it's not that.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_81e8d9b0}"
    new "\"I'm just glad that we managed to get everything done.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f02be5f5}"
    new "\"I see.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5a91cda4}"
    new "\"I am, too.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b61a45fa}"
    new "\"I was a little concerned about time...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_744cb23b}"
    new "\"I need to start making dinner soon.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_93deaf69_3}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_35d0e327}"
    new "\"So you don't have any time left?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cf07af8c}"
    new "I was secretly hoping we would have extra time after finishing the work..."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a0913b0a}"
    new "\"Well...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_71a86863}"
    new "\"...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9e1d344c}"
    new "Yuri thinks to herself."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_374f5df8}"
    new "\"I-I think it would be too irresponsible of me to wait much longer...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_6e8213df}"
    new "\"I'm sorry!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_14634e1c}"
    new "\"I was hoping there would be more time as well...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_0bcd6754}"
    new "\"It's probably my fault.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ec3b86ed}"
    new "\"Sorry for being such a slow worker.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2d19a7fc}"
    new "\"No, it's not your fault at all.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b720218b}"
    new "\"And...the important thing is that we got everything done, right?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_69c25b65}"
    new "\"Yeah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d6c08456}"
    new "\"So...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_86ced03c}"
    new "\"I shouldn't be disappointed...or anything.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_8208851f}"
    new "Gathering all her things, Yuri seems to look a little downcast."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_de976283}"
    new "I understand why."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1675b7da}"
    new "It sounded like she rarely gets the opportunity to spend time with friends in a relaxed environment."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_199cbd75}"
    new "But that doesn't mean this is the last time it can happen..."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1c6f46bc}"
    new "Once Yuri packs up, I walk her out the front door."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_e25c257e}"
    new "\"Thank you very much for having me today.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_63623610}"
    new "\"No problem, I'm glad I was able to help.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_58c510ae}"
    new "\"Just let me know if there's anything else you need me to bring tomorrow.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2ad5f7b3}"
    new "\"I will.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_4f72802e}"
    new "\"Well, then...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_b0923a1d}"
    new "Yuri fidgets."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7c27ec04}"
    new "\"I guess...I'll see you tomorrow.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c67f99c5}"
    new "\"Wait--\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f08fa8ca}"
    new "I kind of say that without thinking."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2a3db547}"
    new "\"About today...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_bbce3672}"
    new "\"It's fine that we didn't have as much time as we wanted.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_3cb990e3}"
    new "\"Because we can do this again.\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_cb29463d}"
    new "\"Whenever you want, you can come over, or we can go out somewhere--\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_a7d20c81}"
    new "\"Ah, I forgot you don't like going out much--\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_dc020e04}"
    new "As I stumble over my words, Yuri simply smiles bashfully."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_7e00e9ab}"
    new "\"Anyway...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_91094ce1}"
    new "\"You know what I'm trying to say, so...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9a0eedea}"
    new "\"You're very thoughtful, [player].\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d2dbb876}"
    new "Yuri takes a step closer to me, then briefly squeezes my hand."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c7ffdf05}"
    new "\"I kind of like that about you...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_c14c584c}"
    new "\"Well...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_97034e8b}"
    new "How am I supposed to respond to that?"

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_078f3436}"
    new "But I don't even get a chance to, as Yuri suddenly pulls back."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d42c29c3}"
    new "\"S-Sayori--?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_af40f385}"
    new "\"Eh?!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_699ac020}"
    new "\"Ah...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_072fe968}"
    new "\"H-Hi, [player]...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_48d5b9aa}"
    new "\"Sayori--!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_5f437551}"
    new "\"Just now, we weren't--\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_67281b29}"
    new "\"Ehehe~\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_9751c7af}"
    new "\"It's okay, [player].\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_22ed0333}"
    new "\"I just stopped by to say hi~\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ce43ac16}"
    new "\"U-Um...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_15104c6c}"
    new "\"Well, it's nice to see you...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_1c747780}"
    new "\"I'm sorry, but I'm already on my way to leave!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2b79f5e2}"
    new "\"Aw, really?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_99f9ae0f}"
    new "\"That's too bad...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_8e9bd95d}"
    new "\"I'm sorry...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_dc3a9a87}"
    new "\"But we'll all be together at the festival tomorrow, so...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_2fc13e16}"
    new "\"So that's fine, right?\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_518ab1c0}"
    new "\"Of course!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_d9a63191}"
    new "Sayori beams."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_f91d45b5}"
    new "\"Y-Yeah, so...\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_86e212e0}"
    new "\"I'll see you tomorrow!\""

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_ee33e5eb}"
    new "Clearly embarrassed, Yuri hurries off."

    old "{#ch4_exclusive_yuri_69c28b16}"
    new "Sayori waves goodbye after her."

    old "{#ch4_end_4de86fac}"
    new "\"Sayori--\""

    old "{#ch4_end_df916532}"
    new "\"I thought you didn't want to come over today!\""

    old "{#ch4_end_0bce81b2}"
    new "\"Ahaha, well...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_c25ef746}"
    new "\"I tried staying in my room...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_dbf79f14}"
    new "\"But my imagination was being really mean to me...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_970496bc}"
    new "\"So I had to come here and see it for myself.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_7b59bc97}"
    new "\"See what?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_3d996037}"
    new "\"What are you talking about?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_f8ac1185}"
    new "\"You know...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_e9eaa5d7}"
    new "\"How much fun you were having with [ch4_name].\""

    old "{#ch4_end_2ce2e237}"
    new "\"And how close you got to her.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_bcdea329}"
    new "\"It makes me...really happy...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_de92f417}"
    new "\"That you've made such good friends.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_194142fb}"
    new "\"That's all that matters to me.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_d97a01d7}"
    new "Tears start to fall down Sayori's face."

    old "{#ch4_end_bedd3333}"
    new "\"That's all that matters to me--!\""

    old "{#ch4_end_cfa94369}"
    new "\"Why am I feeling this way, [player]?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_c4296c1b}"
    new "\"I'm supposed to be happy for you.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_94ef81d5}"
    new "\"Why does it feel like my heart is splitting in half?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_62fe0236}"
    new "\"It hurts so much...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_f290081d}"
    new "\"Everything hurts so much...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_a6de14fb}"
    new "\"This would be so much better if I could just disappear!\""

    old "{#ch4_end_9d6ea3d7}"
    new "\"Sayori, don't say that!\""

    old "{#ch4_end_024365d0}"
    new "\"It's true, [player]!\""

    old "{#ch4_end_4e3bfbbd}"
    new "\"If I wasn't here, then you wouldn't have to waste your sympathy on me!\""

    old "{#ch4_end_e8ab76f3}"
    new "\"You wouldn't have to put up with me being selfish!\""

    old "{#ch4_end_bb805239}"
    new "\"Monika was right...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_427d4d4f}"
    new "\"I should just...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_bddde58a}"
    new "\"Monika...?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_c7aa397f}"
    new "\"Monika was right about what?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_e1554201}"
    new "\"...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_e87e0575}"
    new "\"Sayori...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_afb11ffe}"
    new "\"What I said before is true.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_35fc502b}"
    new "\"I'm not going to let this continue.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_993d9b77}"
    new "\"Caring about you like this isn't the burden your mind is making it out to be.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_adc9cfd4}"
    new "\"It's something that makes me happy.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_4516b61a}"
    new "\"It's something that I wouldn't trade for anything else.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_900cd81d}"
    new "\"So, even if it takes an entire lifetime...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_ad66a1ec}"
    new "\"I'm going to be by your side until you don't feel any more pain.\""

    old "{#ch4_end_023a56fd}"
    new "\"B-But...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_6d934958}"
    new "Sayori looks away."

    old "{#ch4_end_77065901}"
    new "I put a hand on her shoulder to reassure her."

    old "{#ch4_end_603c500f}"
    new "\"I'm scared, [player]...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_16db0b05}"
    new "\"I'm really scared...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_8409288d}"
    new "\"What are you scared of, Sayori?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_5dfc374d}"
    new "\"I'm scared that...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_6c58de13}"
    new "\"That I might like you more than you like me...\""

    old "{#ch4_end_e47a0e88}"
    new "\"Sayori...?\""

    old "{#ch4_end_4ef04544}"
    new "\"It's true, isn't it?\""

